The '''Three Great Tenjin Shrines''' (日本三大天神) are a group of three [[Shinto]] shrines dedicated to [[Tenjin (kami)|Tenjin]], the deified form of the scholar-courtier [[Sugawara no Michizane]]. They are traditionally enumerated as:

*[[Dazaifu Tenman-gū]], [[Dazaifu, Fukuoka]] Prefecture
*[[Hōfu Tenman-gū]], [[Yamaguchi Prefecture]]
*[[Kitano Tenman-gū]], [[Kyoto]]

